    <h1>About This Directory</h1>

    <p>
      The Coal Region Death Care Directory is a free community resource for families in Schuylkill County, Pennsylvania. We list every locally-owned funeral home, cemetery, cremation service, and monument company serving the Coal Region.
    </p>

    <h2>Why We Built This</h2>
    <p>
      When a family experiences a loss, finding the right provider shouldn't require hours of searching. Schuylkill County is unique — every single funeral home here is locally owned and operated. There are no national chains. These are your neighbors, serving families they've known for generations.
    </p>
    <p>
      We wanted to make it easier for families to find, compare, and contact these providers, especially during moments when clarity matters most.
    </p>

    <h2>What We Include</h2>
    <p>
      Every listing includes publicly available information: name, address, phone number, website, and Google ratings. We don't accept payment for placement or rankings — listings are organized alphabetically by city.
    </p>

    <h2>About Antigravity</h2>
    <p>
      This directory is maintained by <strong>Antigravity</strong>, a digital services company helping local businesses in the Coal Region strengthen their online presence. We believe that the businesses serving families during their most difficult moments deserve modern tools to reach the people who need them.
    </p>

    <p>
      <a href="/contact/">Have a question or correction? Contact us.</a>
    </p>
